---
import LegalLayout from '../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
import { SITE, LEGAL } from '../consts';
---
<LegalLayout title="Terms of Use" description="The terms and conditions for using MoveWell Reviews.">
  <p class="notice">This page is a starting template, not legal advice — have a qualified attorney review it before launch.</p>

  <p class="lead">
    These Terms of Use ("Terms") govern your access to and use of {SITE.name} ({SITE.domain}),
    operated by {LEGAL.entity}. By using the site, you agree to these Terms. If you don't agree,
    please don't use the site.
  </p>

  <h2>1. Editorial content, not professional advice</h2>
  <p>
    Content on this site — including reviews, ratings, and buying guides — reflects our own opinions
    based on hands-on testing and research. It is provided for general informational purposes only
    and is <strong>not medical, fitness, or professional advice</strong>. Consult a qualified
    professional before starting any exercise or recovery routine, especially if you have a
    pre-existing health condition. See our <a href="/disclaimer">Disclaimer</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>2. Accuracy, pricing &amp; availability</h2>
  <p>
    Product specifications, availability, and pricing change frequently and are controlled by the
    retailers we link to, not by us. We do not display live prices; a link labeled "Check current
    price" takes you to the retailer, where current pricing is shown. We try to keep information
    current but make no guarantee of accuracy at the time you read it — always verify details on the
    merchant's site before purchasing.
  </p>

  <h2>3. Affiliate links</h2>
  <p>
    This site contains affiliate links and we may earn a commission when you buy through them, at no
    extra cost to you. See our <a href="/affiliate-disclosure">Affiliate Disclosure</a> for details.
  </p>

  <h2>4. Acceptable use</h2>
  <p>You agree not to misuse the site, including by attempting to breach security, scrape content at scale, disrupt the service, or use it for any unlawful purpose.</p>

  <h2>5. Intellectual property</h2>
  <p>
    Unless otherwise noted, text, graphics, and original photography on this site are owned by
    {LEGAL.entity} and may not be copied or republished without permission. Product images and
    trademarks belong to their respective owners and are used for identification and commentary
    purposes.
  </p>

  <h2>6. Third-party sites</h2>
  <p>
    We are not responsible for the content, policies, or practices of third-party sites you reach
    through links on {SITE.domain}, including retailers and affiliate networks.
  </p>

  <h2>7. Disclaimer of warranties</h2>
  <p>
    The site is provided "as is" and "as available" without warranties of any kind, express or
    implied, including merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, and non-infringement.
  </p>

  <h2>8. Limitation of liability</h2>
  <p>
    To the fullest extent permitted by law, {LEGAL.entity} and its contributors are not liable for
    any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of the site or reliance
    on its content, including purchasing decisions made based on our reviews.
  </p>

  <h2>9. Indemnification</h2>
  <p>You agree to indemnify and hold {LEGAL.entity} harmless from any claims arising out of your misuse of the site or violation of these Terms.</p>

  <h2>10. Governing law</h2>
  <p>
    These Terms are governed by the laws of the State of {LEGAL.governingState}, United States,
    without regard to its conflict-of-law principles. Any dispute will be resolved in the courts
    located in {LEGAL.governingState}.
  </p>

  <h2>11. Changes</h2>
  <p>We may revise these Terms at any time; continued use of the site after changes take effect means you accept the revised Terms.</p>

  <h2>12. Contact</h2>
  <p>Questions? Reach us at <a href={`mailto:${LEGAL.legalEmail}`}>{LEGAL.legalEmail}</a>.</p>
</LegalLayout>
